{"tid":1910523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Luke de Pulford : 英國在政治上是不可能收回香港的","createTime":"2020-03-04T17:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T17:44:19.000Z","uid":53844,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0d20af93f2b2983836ae0cee6660dbeb7ee328","tid":1910523,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"人們問，鑑於中國違反《聯合聲明》，香港能否重歸英國主權。<br />\nPeople asking if Hong Kong can be returned to British sovereignty in light of violations of the Joint Declaration by China. <br />\n<br />\n答：即使在法律上有可能&ldquo;重新殖民&rdquo;香港（不是），在政治上也是不可能的。<br />\nAnswer: even if it were legally possible to &ldquo;re-colonise&rdquo; HK (it isn&rsquo;t), it wouldn&rsquo;t be politically possible. <br />\n<br />\n不要浪費時間考慮這個問題... <br />\nDon&rsquo;t waste time thinking about this...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1235248779198181377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1235248779198181377&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbICKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=5970f399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1235248779198181377&h=29694071\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1235248779198181377</a>"},{"pid":"828d28be87e1b8ad5e458f6dee6500fba4c52efc","tid":1910523,"uid":53844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"...when so much help is needed. <br />\n<br />\nE.g. what should the UN protocol be when the JD is violated? It is, after all, a treaty lodged at the UN - Member states have a responsibility to guard it. <br />\nRelevant precedent? <br />\nRemember the U.K. accepts there has been at least one violation. 2/4"},{"pid":"7cfa0fcd32550a09d35e1d3d995eea9c62b173e1","tid":1910523,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"Where is the repository of material setting out<br />\n<br />\n a) what parties thought universal suffrage meant AT THE TIME of negotiation<br />\n<br />\nb) whether the prospect of violation of the JD was ever raised? <br />\n<br />\nThere&rsquo;s no systematic open-source archive. <br />\n<br />\nAny volunteers?"},{"pid":"15ab37e83eef3270fb957ff19dc50406653878fd","tid":1910523,"uid":46042,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"冇人叫佢收回<br />\n<br />\n叫佢比居留權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2514923a12b0143ec078599289db0538754d32e2","tid":1910523,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"It&rsquo;s very tempting to try to find a silver bullet for this problem. There isn&rsquo;t one. <br />\n<br />\nFriends, unless we are careful, a lot of time and energy will be wasted discussing things that simply aren&rsquo;t possible. Let&rsquo;s refocus and channel our energies into more fruitful initiatives."},{"pid":"bd65ac9fe1ae06fc3c0d0b9f35600cee7f8462f4","tid":1910523,"uid":46042,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"其實英國不如收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n香港重有錢過佢<br />\n成日扮晒嘢 以為啲人好想去佢哋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4ed700c3b35c6d4e52a62e52c4debc7fcc432e","tid":1910523,"uid":32204,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"15ab37e83eef3270fb957ff19dc50406653878fd","tid":1910523,"uid":46042,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"冇人叫佢收回<br />\n<br />\n叫佢比居留權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"出面仲有好多人叫歸英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f8cb3518af7ce02ac564bba99b1bb97e7cc5bd","tid":1910523,"uid":236414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15ab37e83eef3270fb957ff19dc50406653878fd",